Q.  Do you expect to see him as the coach next year?

ROD BRIND'AMOUR:   I don't even know if I will be back here next year.  Last thing in my mind is worrying about what is going to be where.  I just want to put this behind me:
 

ROD BRIND'AMOUR:   I mean, I don't really know what to say.  They were so superior in the series.  It wasn't just a defensive game.  It was offensive, it was a lot of things.  It is just -- like I said, they were just a better hockey club.


